uk.co.strangeskies.reflection

Class IntersectionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.reflection.IntersectionType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.reflect.Type

    public abstract class IntersectionType
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.reflect.Type
    An intersection type, as described in the Java 8 language specification. Roughly, such a type generally behaves as a class which extends each of its component types, but is otherwise an empty definition.
